question: Within a radius of 80 kilometers, where can I find  a fast food restaurant in the direction of Dominion Plastic Surgery, Falls Church, VA from Go Fish, Rosedale, MD?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-76.48474 39.339761)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-77.222205 38.878159)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'fast_food'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-76.48474 39.339761)',4326)::geography, 80000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-76.48474 39.339761)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
